  "data": {
    "title": "Pylon Tutorial: Streamline Your B2B Support Step-by-Step",
    "excerpt": "Follow this step-by-step Pylon tutorial to centralize Slack, email & Teams support with AI. See how to set it up and transform your B2B customer service.",
