      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 4: Setting Up Workflows & Macros",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "To scale effectively, you need to systematize the predictable. Pylon’s workflow engine lets you build powerful automations with a simple “if this, then that” logic.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Example Workflow for a Critical Outage:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1.  ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "IF",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " a ticket is tagged “service-outage” in any channel.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2.  ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "THEN",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " auto-assign it to your senior engineering support lead.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3.  ",
            "marks": []
