        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 5: Reporting & Continuous Improvement",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What gets measured gets managed. Pylon’s analytics go beyond basic volume metrics.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Channel Performance:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " See which channel (Slack, email, Teams) generates the most tickets, which has the fastest resolution time, and where clients prefer to engage. This data can inform your team’s resource allocation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Agent Performance:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Track metrics like first response time, resolution time, and ticket volume per agent to identify coaching opportunities and top performers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Customer Health Signals:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Look at trends in ticket topics. A sudden spike in “API integration” tickets might indicate a need for better documentation or a webinar, turning support interactions into product feedback.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Regularly review these reports to identify bottlenecks and refine your workflows. The platform makes it easy to export data for deeper analysis if needed.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
